descriptionHtml:
Go2Joy is a new hourly/daily hotel booking app, fast, convenient, & private. No need to waste time to find a best hotel around you !

Looking for a good hotel around you ? You can check other users’ Rate & Review on each hotels before making a decision.

Book a hotel with Go2Joy before it’s all sold out ! Just a few touches in a few seconds, you can book a hotel without hassle.

Let modern technology to serve you ! Your life will be easier and more comfortable!

Go2Joy is very simple to use and it’s fun. You can just follow these steps:

App Installation :

- Download Go2Joy app onto your mobile phone.

- Allow Notifications for Promotion, Event, New hotels, and much more.

Look for information:

- Open Go2Joy and see the hotels Nearby your current location or choose any other area you want to.

- Go2Joy will introduce hundreds of places in the area you choose with attractive promotions.

Using the service:

- Select a place to go, you will see the full picture, price information, address and directions to the hotel

- Select the time and the room you want to book

- Pay with flexible payment type you like. Go2Joy encourage you prepay to secure the room.

- Remember to check-in to the app upon arrival to receive the benefit from Go2Joy.

After using:

- You can rate and leave a review on the hotel so that we can improve the quality of serving you next time.

- You can mark your favorite location/hotel and introduce your friends to use Go2Joy. We will send you the exciting prizes.

Download the app and experience Go2Joy !
